information: The company BUCHNER & SOHN INH. HERBERT BUCHNER GMBH & CO KG, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1899, which operates in the Shellfish and crustaceans industry. It also operates in the Fish, Meat, Offal, and Meats, cooked and cured industries. It is based in Landshut, Germany.
